  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd \u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The death of a mother elephant fell into a pit with her calf",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Officials of the Wildlife Department said that a wild elephant fell into a pit with its calf in Mahakumbukadawala area and the calf is alive.",
        "The wildlife control unit said that the said wild elephant had entered the village in search of food three days ago and fell into the pit.",
        "The wildlife control department said that while the post-mortem examination of the dead elephant will be conducted on the 21st on the 21st, the baby elephant will be rescued alive and released in the Anuradhapuram Elephant Sanctuary.",
        "The wildlife control department further said that the dead elephant was about 25 years old and the baby elephant was 4 months old."
      ],
